data.description: Beautiful large corner lot home nestled in the well established community of Creek Crossing Estates. No HOA. This home has a rare 4 bedroom floorplan with first floor master bedroom. The living room boasts with tall ceilings, natural light, and a brick fireplace. Kitchen features a gas range, built-in microwave and breakfast bar. Huge fully fenced back yard with patio and storage shed. Located in a great area of Mesquite with convenient access to schools, shopping, entertainment, and employment centers.
